This species was collected as vagrant on leaves of pistachio tree, 
<taxonomicName box="[1267,1436,789,817]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Anacardiaceae" genus="Pistacia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Sapindales" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vera">
<emphasis box="[1267,1436,789,817]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Pistacia vera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. (
<taxonomicName box="[204,401,825,854]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Anacardiaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Sapindales" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Anacardiaceae</taxonomicName>
). Seventeen (17) females and 
<specimenCount box="[829,974,825,854]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" type="male">five males</specimenCount>
, Faculty of Agriculture, 
<collectingRegion box="[1324,1436,826,854]" country="Iran" name="Lorestan" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Lorestan</collectingRegion>
University, 
<date box="[302,495,862,891]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" value="2018-08-09">9 August 2018</date>
; 
<collectingRegion box="[508,745,862,891]" country="Iran" name="Lorestan" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Lorestan Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[757,813,862,890]" name="Iran" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Iran</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="115" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,935,1001]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,308,935,963]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Remarks –</emphasis>
This species was reported from 
<collectingRegion box="[771,1116,935,964]" country="Iran" name="Azarbayjan-e Sharqi" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">East Azarbaijan Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1136,1188,936,964]" name="Iran" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Iran</collectingCountry>
for the first time (
<bibRefCitation author="Lotfollahi, P. &amp; de Lillo, E. &amp; Haddad Irani-Nejad, K." box="[160,453,972,1001]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" pagination="17 - 27" refId="ref4137" refString="Lotfollahi, P., de Lillo, E. &amp; Haddad Irani-Nejad, K. (2014 a) Three new species from the subfamily Phyllocoptinae (Acari, Trombidiformes, Eriophyidae) in Iran. ZooKeys, 426: 17 - 27. DOI: 10.3897 / zookeys. 426.8087" type="journal article" year="2014">
Lotfollahi 
<emphasis box="[298,354,972,1001]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">et al</emphasis>
. 2014a
</bibRefCitation>
). This is the first record of this species from 
<collectingRegion box="[1025,1262,972,1001]" country="Iran" name="Lorestan" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Lorestan Province</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
